com.pkware.smartcrypt.metaclient

Class UpgradeStateNotification

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pkware.smartcrypt.metaclient.Notification
      • com.pkware.smartcrypt.metaclient.UpgradeStateNotification

  • public final class UpgradeStateNotification
extends Notification
    Indicates that Smartcrypt data using features not familiar to this version of the SDK have been found. The impact of these new features can range from simple being "nice to have" features to being features that prevent this version of the SDK from working with the data. The Notification.priority can be either NotificationPriority.PROBLEM or NotificationPriority.NOTICE depending on the severity. The Notification.message will have more detailed information for a human user to understand.
